stories.description: Super Admin navigates to the menu mapping page to activate specific menu items. This ensures that the correct menus are available for users based on their roles.
stories.expected_outcome:
Selected menu items are activated and reflected in the menu settings.

VALIDATION: Assert: toggles are in the active state. Assert: confirmation dialog closes after activation.

steps.target: Step 1: Navigate to the menu mapping page
Step 2: Click 'more_vert' to open the menu options
Step 3: Click 'Tindakan' to view actions
Step 4: Toggle 'mat-mdc-slide-toggle-0-button' to activate
Step 5: Click 'Ok' to confirm
Step 6: Verify that the toggle is in the active state

stories.user_persona: Ministry Admin searching for specific menu items
stories.description: Ministry Admin uses the search functionality to find specific menu items and then resets the filters to view all items again.
stories.expected_outcome:
Search results display only items related to 'Dashboard'. Filters are reset to show all items.

VALIDATION: Assert: table shows only 'Dashboard' related items after search. Assert: all items are displayed after reset.

steps.target: Step 1: Navigate to the menu mapping page
Step 2: Fill 'Cari' with 'Dashboard'
Step 3: Click 'Cari' to search
Step 4: Verify search results show 'Dashboard' related items
Step 5: Click 'Reset' to clear filters
Step 6: Verify all items are displayed

stories.description: Mosque Admin deactivates specific menu items to ensure only relevant menus are visible to users.
stories.expected_outcome:
Selected menu items are deactivated and no longer visible in the menu settings.

VALIDATION: Assert: toggles are in the inactive state. Assert: confirmation dialog closes after deactivation.

steps.target: Step 1: Navigate to the menu mapping page
Step 2: Click 'more_vert' to open the menu options
Step 3: Click 'Tindakan' to view actions
Step 4: Toggle 'mat-mdc-slide-toggle-20-button' to deactivate
Step 5: Click 'Ok' to confirm
Step 6: Verify that the toggle is in the inactive state

stories.description: Super Admin navigates through different menu settings to verify that configurations are correctly applied and visible.
stories.expected_outcome:
Menu settings are correctly displayed and reflect the current configurations.

VALIDATION: Assert: all menu items are displayed with correct configurations. Assert: navigation between pages is smooth.

steps.target: Step 1: Navigate to the menu mapping page
Step 2: Click 'Next page' to navigate through menu settings
Step 3: Verify that menu settings are displayed correctly
Step 4: Click 'Previous page' to return
Step 5: Verify that navigation is smooth and settings are consistent
